* There's some scrolling which is annoying. Can you change the window size setting in the settings.json file?
*Is there any way you can make it so you can go back and listen only to the part the puppet says? At some point I found myself tuning out, and then I had to rewatch the whole video which was pretty annoying. Maybe you could only enable the skipping after it's played through once?
*Just out of curiosity, what is up with the different things you sometimes say after the stimuli, since they aren't always the same (e.g. she took that but not that because it was too heavy)? Also -- was the "that" part of the original script? Cause I think it would sound a lot better if you said "that one and  not that one"
